Target : Hassio 

What This Does: 
Check configuration, if ok restart hassio

How It Does This:
A script is set up to run a shell command.
If check config is ok, it executes the restart command.
Else, it reports back to Hassio via the Webhook component. 

Steps to Use
1. Copy check_restart into /config
2. Run "chmod +x /config/check_restart/" in your terminal to make it executable
3. Edit check_restart and enter your Domain name
4. Copy relevant parts of configuration.yaml
